No wonder vegetarian food has a bad name.
We visited this location twice, the first time I left reasonably happy due to the complimentary chocolate-covered strawberries,  friendly staff, and fresh, vibrant produce.
I appreciated the build-my-own salad, but got a bit frustrated when I was told 'no substitutions' on the sandwiches.
